    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>地よ、水よ、火よ、風よ、
天理なす配合を乱し
壊劫（えこう）を招来せよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Earth, Water, Fire, and Wind. Throw
the natural order out of balance.
Allow the Maha-Kalpa to end.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>地よ、水よ、火よ、風よ、
天理なす……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Earth, Water, Fire, and Wind.
Throw the natural order...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何、呪文がこだまして……
これが暴走の正体……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's this chant saying?
So...this is the truth behind
the Mana rampage...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この声が消えない限りは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If this voice stops casting this spell...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>声……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A voice...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>音を司り、それを操る精霊、
グラムロックだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are none other than the ruler of
sound. Your true name is Glamrock,
the Summon Spirit of Sound.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もしかしたら……
ぼくの力で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe...I can use my power...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300240</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>多くの過ちがゆえ……
我がおまえから記憶を奪った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This small one has committed too
many sins... It was by my hand
that its memories were erased.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、記憶も戻ってきて
もしぼくが今と違うぼくに
なっちゃったラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...If my memories return, what
if I become someone else entirely?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ううん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのふたりには……
もうお母さんはいらない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those two have grown...They
don't need a mother anymore!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから……旅の最後くらい、
ぼくの可愛い双子のために
なれば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why...at the end of our
journey...I will do this for my
fair pair of twins...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼく……
ふたりの力になりたい……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I will become their power!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだ、ぼくは……
音の精霊……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...It's coming back to me...
I'm the Spirit of Sound...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>鎮めよ、言霊（ことだま）、
我が眷属となり、
我が元に集い来ん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Silence, O magic of Logos,
submit thyself, and return
unto me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えぇいっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haaaah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>地よ、水よ、火よ、風よ、
天理なす配合を乱し
壊劫を……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Earth, Water, Fire, and Wind. Throw
the natural order out of balance.
Allow the Maha-Ka...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301204</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;！　&lt;Mel&gt;！
聞こえる！？　今だよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;! &lt;Mel&gt;! Can you
hear me!? Try now!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……な、何が
あったんだよ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What's going on!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……わかんない……
でも……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I don't know, but...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊よ！　もう一度！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Summon Spirits! Do your thing again!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
